### A donation from you today could help us understand the causes of diabetes,
enable people to prevent or manage their condition, and eventually find a
Text to donate is the easiest way to give to us – using your mobile phone. It
only takes a few seconds to make a big difference.
It only takes a few seconds to make a big difference.
**Text DUK to 70002 to donate £3 a month**
**Text DUK to 70088 to donate £5 a month**
* Monthly donations are taken directly from your phone bill.
* You will receive a free reminder text each month, 24 hours before your donation is deducted.
* To skip a monthly donation text SKIP, or simply do nothing to continue your monthly donations.
You can stop your donations at any time by texting STOP to 70002 or call 020
## How to make a one off donation
* Shortly after you text us, we’ll send you a Thank you message from 70507 to let you know we’ve received your generous donation. 
* The donation will be deducted straight from your phone bill for this month
#### Where can I send text donations from?
This service is available in England, Scotland, Northern Ireland and Wales
only. You must obtain permission from the bill payer before sending a text
message. If you are under 16 years old, you must have your parent or
guardian's permission to send an SMS donation to us.
#### Cost of donations by text and what we receive
The amount you donated will be taken from your phone bill plus the cost of one
text message at your standard network rate (usually 4p). So for example if you
text DUK to 70123 to give £5 you will be charged £5.04. Diabetes UK will
#### How to contact us or change how we communicate with you
You can change how you hear from us or ask us to stop communicating with you
Details of your donation including your personal data will be collected by
Mobilise (Open Mobile Global Ltd 2017). Mobilise is a donation management
platform commissioned by Diabetes UK Ltd. Your data will be stored securely in
line with relevant data protection provisions for the purpose of processing
payments only and will not be kept longer than necessary. For further
information about how Mobilise will process your data see their privacy notice
We'd love to keep you updated about how we support people living with diabetes
and how you can help by donating, volunteering and campaigning. By texting DUK
to 70123 you are agreeing to us staying in touch with you by post and phone.
Occasionally we may need to share personal data with our suppliers to process
your orders and requests or to provide other services to us.
*Calls to 0345 numbers cost no more than calls to geographic (01 and 02) numbers and must be included in inclusive minutes on mobile phones and discount schemes. Calls from landlines are typically charged between 2p and 10p per minute while calls from mobiles typically cost between 10p and 40p per minute. Calls from landlines and mobiles to 0345 numbers are included in free call packages. Calls may be recorded for quality and training purposes.
